<HEADLINE> Marthas Son Wins Queen Mother Race </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, March 12 (Xinhua) -- Marthas Son having only its second
 race in 15 months won the Queen Mother Champion Chase in
Cheltenham, Britain, on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Ask Tom was second with two time Champion Chase winner Viking
Flagship in third and last year's Irish trained winner Klairon
Davis a distant fourth. 
</P>
