<HEADLINE> Bankruptcies in Germany in 1996 Reach New Record </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BONN, March 12 (Xinhua) -- Bankruptcies in Germany in 1996
reached a fourth straight record high of 31,471 cases, or 9.3
percent more than those of 1995, the Federal Statistics Office
said today.
</P>
