all these demand cooperation with Portugal, the minister noted.
</P>
<P>
Under the assistance of the World Bank, he said, four roads in
Luanda's suburbs would also be built, at a cost of some 25
million U.S. Dollars. And the European Union will assist in
building a 70-km road in the south, he added. 
