low ebb this week. King Hussein sent a letter to Prime
Minister Binyamin Netanyahu on March 9 saying that the premier
is not acting as a peace partner and instead his policies,
especially building a Jewish settlement in East Jerusalem, will
make bloodshed virtually inevitable.
</P>
