"distant, elusive mirage."
</P>
<P>
In a three-page response to the monarch sent on March 10,
Netanyahu sought to defend Israel's policies and called for
Israeli-Jordanian relations and their own personal relationship not
to be held hostage to Palestinian-Israeli negotiations. 
