<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, March 13 (Xinhua) -- Indian External Affairs
Minister I.K. Gujral said today that the United Nations must put
an end to domination of muscle and money.
</P>
<P>
Inaugurating a seminar on the relationship between India and
the U.N., Gujral said the world body must be rescued from its
present state of uncertainties and made truly democratic. He did
not, however, specify which country has manipulated the world
body.
</P>
