has made in economic construction, adding that China's economic
growth has provided more opportunities for his company's
cooperation with China.
</P>
<P>
Jiang and Gerstner also exchanged views on the future
development of global information industry.
</P>
<P>
Gerstner is on a working visit to China at the invitation of
the Chinese Ministry of Electronics Industry. 
