<DOCNO> XIE19970313.0194 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-03-13 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Revisions Made to Two Drafts under NPC Deliberation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 13 (Xinhua) -- Revisions have been made to draft
amendments to the Criminal Law and a draft Defense Law at the
suggestions of deputies before the two drafts are put to a vote by
the National People's Congress (NPC), which has been in session
since March 1.
</P>
<P>
Xue Ju, chairman of NPC Law Committee, delivered a report on
the results of deputies' deliberations of the two drafts and a
draft method for the election of deputies from the Hong Kong
Special Administrative Region (SAR) to the Ninth NPC, at the third
meeting of the presidium of the Fifth Session of the Eighth NPC
today.
</P>
<P>
The report was adopted by the presidium.
</P>
<P>
The deputies held that the draft amendments to the Criminal Law
conform basically with actual conditions in the country, and will
be conducive to combating crime, protecting people, and
safeguarding the smooth progression of socialist reform,
opening-up and modernization, said Xue.
</P>
<P>
The enactment of a defense law is of great significance for
strengthening national defense, safeguarding national sovereignty
and unity, and territorial integrity and safety, he said.
</P>
<P>
He said the deputies thus suggest that the NPC session adopt the
two drafts with some revisions.
</P>
<P>
The deputies have agreed to the draft method for the election
of deputies from the HKSAR to the Ninth NPC, and suggested that it
be approved by the session.
</P>
<P>
Based on proposals put forth by deputies, Xue said, the Law
Committee has made several revisions to the draft criminal law and
the draft defense law.
</P>
<P>
The committee has added to the draft amendments to the Criminal
Law provisions on hijacking of vessels and automobiles, loan
sharking (getting loans in an illegal way, then re-loan it to
other people for illegal profit), inclusion in publications of
content that insults the customs of ethnic minorities, and
smuggling, trafficking, transporting, manufacturing and illegal
possession of "ice."
</P>
<P>
Given the fact that loan sharking has run rampant and seriously
disrupted financial market order, the committee has decided to add
the provision to the draft.
</P>
<P>
For those smuggling, trafficking, transporting, and possessing
"ice" illegally, the added provision stipulate that punishment be
the same as that for the same amount of heroin smuggled,
trafficked, transported or possessed illegally.
</P>
<P>
The revised draft defense law makes stipulations on carrying
out defense education, guaranteeing the legitimate rights and
interests of servicemen, and their welfare, said Xue.
</P>
<P>
Since the Criminal Law contains an article on the crime of
endangering the interests of national defense, the Law Committee
has deleted the chapter on legal responsibilities in the draft
defense law, and added in its general rules this provision: "those
who violate this law and related laws by refusing to perform their
duties in defense or endangering the interests of national
defense, shall be investigated and bear legal responsibilities."
</P>
<P>
The committee also added the stipulation that "this law's
provisions on servicemen are applicable to the Chinese People's
Armed Police Force."
</P>
<P>
According to Xue Ju, the deputies have expressed their approval
of the draft method for the election of deputies from HKSAR to the
Ninth NPC, and the Law Committee has also agreed to its
stipulations and no revision was suggested.  
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
