business and future of the Non-Aligned Movement with Indian
leaders. South Africa will take over chairmanship of the
100-member NAM in 1998. NAM foreign ministers are scheduled to
meet here early next month.
</P>
<P>
Mandela will be here after taking part in the 25th anniversary
celebrations of Bangladesh's independence on March 26.  
