<HEADLINE> Sri Lankan Schools to Be Closed For Elections </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
COLOMBO, March 13 (Xinhua) -- Sri Lankan schools selected as
polling stations for the forthcoming local government elections
due to be held on March 21 will be closed on March 20 and 21,
according to Education Ministry sources today.
