"China Daily"
</P>
<P>
-- State Councillor Peng Peiyun called on the people Wednesday
to follow the late Deng Xiaoping's theory on population growth in
moving the country's family planning drive to a new level.
</P>
<P>
Speaking at the close of the five-day national conference on
family planning, she warned that family planning workers should
not rest on previous achievements or be blindly optimistic over
population figures.
</P>
