for the 21st century was presented to a symposium that opened in
Beijing Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Zhang Kunming, Deputy Director of the National Environmental
Protection Agency said at the symposium's opening ceremony that
the report will also help the World Bank and other bilateral
multilateral agencies decide whether or not to grant
environment-related assistance to China. 
